Coming to  the mobile technology for which the company Samsung famous for , Samsung may not be the first company  to make a smartphone, but it was one of the first players to truly get aggressive about the market, introducing the first “PDA phone( Personal Digital Assistant)” with a color display in the U.S. market at the year 2001.called the SPH-i300.
<br>
<br>
Wow, things sure have changed a lot since then…
<br>In 2006, the company has been largest  manufacturer of televisions  in terms of specs ,and in the beginning of  2010, the Galaxy series expanded a lot from a smartphone to tablet computers  with all the advanced specs needed at that time.
After many struggles and downfalls in its designs,configurations ,applications samsung set its foot as world’s no 1 smart phone maker overtaking apple in the year 2012.
<br><br>
Samsung offers its employees a home away from a home to allow teams ,to focus completely on the ideas as they explore more and share ideas.
For the bordeaux project,the team studied what consumers really want in a television. They discovered that many want a TV that looks good from every angle like a “sparkling glass of fine wine.beautiful shape .beautiful colour”. Introduced in 2007,the bordeaux went on to become the world’s most desired LCD TV. more than one million sets were sold in the first 6 months crossing the margin of 3 million.
After all it started with a ”glass of wine”……
Have you got inspiration after reading the above story !  that the success of all the great technology that evolved today got started from the basic idea…… </p>

