Besides, the other focus areas are Augmented Reality, Virtual Reality, Artificial intelligence, multi-device connectivity, and services like payment and health. Recently , the company have  launched a virtual reality head gear called Gear VR for Galaxy Note 4. This was another global product the India R&D team worked on. 
